replies.body:
So, the problem isn't rage blade, it's "sated?" So then the next thing I would recommend is checking out exactly what sated does. 

Every other auto attack applies "on-hit" effects a second time. Well, that sounds to me like less AA's = less proc's.

{{item:3110}}

 {{item:3143}} 

Since the magic damage isn't "that much," armor should help you more than MR as well. The little extra bit of health will also allow you to use whatever escape mechanics you may have. If you don't have any, you now have an item that slows movement speed.
